Islam Leaves Highbridge, Rejoins Third Point, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-19T00:53:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-18/highbridge-capital-s-islam-quits-to-rejoin-three-point-ft-says.html
(Corrects name of firm.)  Munib Islam, former head of European
equities at Highbridge Capital Management LLC, has quit the
hedge fund and rejoined Third Point LLC -- the firm he left
three years ago -- as head of equities research, the Financial
Times reported, citing two people familiar with the matter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
